    <title>春游</title>
    <link href="/2021/04/18/%E6%98%A5%E6%B8%B8/"/>
    <url>/2021/04/18/%E6%98%A5%E6%B8%B8/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>一口气溜到树枝端的阿彪，集体颜艺小游戏，摄协的传统拍合照，还有“抢”着吃辣条的体验都在这次的春游活动里面了。</p></blockquote><hr> <span id="more"></span><p>摄协传统：　 <img src="https://static01.imgkr.com/temp/fbeab6c424f5479db663522d1bfa7009.jpg" alt="合照" style="zoom:80%;" /><br>500多块都躺在刚买的野餐垫上了，蛋糕，披萨看着挺好吃的，但大家都抢着拿辣条。<br><img src="https://static01.imgkr.com/temp/3286b3e654534752ab7834d1ad4e17dc.jpg" alt="辣条" style="zoom:80%;" />角色互换，阿彪摄影师被会长御用模特拍了近一小时。<br><img src="https://static01.imgkr.com/temp/c9f6b4193ece48508cda9b7ec6fb8489.jpg" alt="模特和她的摄影师" style="zoom:80%;" />已经忘了是谁怂恿阿彪上树当模特，等我们反应过来时他已经溜了半截（专业人士，请勿模仿）<br><img src="https://static01.imgkr.com/temp/f457f4f463b741739bca053cd9f384c7.jpg" alt="阿彪~" style="zoom:80%;" /><br><img src="https://static01.imgkr.com/temp/5579981c4fc04580b0add47fd8ccac1d.jpg" alt="呲牙咧嘴" style="zoom:80%;" /></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
